WEBVTT

01:40.380 --> 01:48.740
[You are My Fateful Love]
[EP03]

01:54.380 --> 01:56.899
How did I even add him?

01:57.380 --> 01:57.940
Well...

01:58.580 --> 01:59.819
What did my friend request

01:59.819 --> 02:00.619
say?

02:19.859 --> 02:21.539
[Hello, Lawyer Xu.]

02:22.380 --> 02:23.699
[This is Ruan Yu.]

02:38.340 --> 02:41.900
[If it's okay with you,]

02:42.579 --> 02:44.979
[I'd like to ask you a question.]

02:46.500 --> 02:47.380
[Well...]

02:48.539 --> 02:50.460
[What did my friend request]

02:50.699 --> 02:51.739
[say?]

03:18.139 --> 03:19.940
[Sorry, Mr. Xu.]

03:20.419 --> 03:22.060
[I accidentally]

03:22.539 --> 03:24.340
[pressed the wrong key.]

03:25.180 --> 03:26.259
[Are you]

03:26.859 --> 03:28.699
[in the US right now?]

03:45.940 --> 03:46.979
[Sorry,]

03:47.460 --> 03:48.380
[I didn't know that.]

03:54.979 --> 03:56.539
[Sorry for disturbing your rest.]

03:57.180 --> 03:58.340
[Let's talk]

03:58.500 --> 03:59.539
[when you're free.]

04:02.539 --> 04:03.900
Wasted that coffee for nothing?

04:10.780 --> 04:13.180
Let's do 5 p.m. San Francisco time.

04:13.900 --> 04:15.139
5 p.m.

04:26.780 --> 04:27.499
8 a.m. Beijing Time?

04:28.660 --> 04:29.859
So as soon as I wake up,

04:29.859 --> 04:30.979
I'll have to talk to him about the case?

04:33.260 --> 04:33.900
It's fine.

04:35.820 --> 04:36.780
At least there's over

04:36.780 --> 04:37.979
ten thousand kilometers between us.

04:38.780 --> 04:39.900
No face-to-face.

05:11.340 --> 05:12.100
It's still early.

05:40.340 --> 05:41.739
So late?

05:52.020 --> 05:53.419
Being a lawyer in California,

05:54.660 --> 05:56.379
Xu Huaisong can't be

05:56.379 --> 05:57.580
that idle, right?

05:59.660 --> 06:01.100
He wouldn't just wait around for me…

06:02.780 --> 06:03.340
Would he?

06:07.900 --> 06:09.179
Mr. Xu, I'm so sorry.

06:09.379 --> 06:10.179
I overslept.

06:10.660 --> 06:11.780
Are you free now?

06:43.059 --> 06:44.419
So shall we start?

06:49.939 --> 06:50.739
[Let's talk face-to-face.]

06:54.299 --> 06:55.859
Isn't he in San Francisco?

06:59.539 --> 07:00.260
[Via video.]

07:06.499 --> 07:08.299
Video call?

07:14.140 --> 07:15.059
[May I ask,]

07:15.260 --> 07:16.379
[is there any part of this case]

07:16.379 --> 07:17.780
[that requires a video meeting?]

07:27.979 --> 07:28.660
[Sorry,]

07:28.739 --> 07:29.700
[I'm not available right now.]

07:34.780 --> 07:35.340
[How long?]

07:41.859 --> 07:43.140
[They say in front of an ex]

07:43.140 --> 07:43.939
[you can't lose your composure.]

07:44.179 --> 07:45.379
[An ex-crush and an ex]

07:45.379 --> 07:46.340
[are just one word apart.]

07:46.900 --> 07:48.499
[I can't look this messy.]

07:54.220 --> 07:55.059
[Ten minutes.]

09:47.340 --> 09:48.420
This is way too casual.

09:51.460 --> 09:52.019
No, no.

10:03.499 --> 10:04.300
Still got time.

10:22.899 --> 10:24.460
Mr. Xu, I'm ready.

10:40.060 --> 10:40.859
Hello.

10:41.779 --> 10:42.820
Your manuscript

10:42.820 --> 10:43.940
is a bit long.

10:44.259 --> 10:45.540
I'll skim through it for now.

10:48.700 --> 10:50.659
Or you can just skip it.

10:51.859 --> 10:52.820
It's well-written.

10:53.460 --> 10:54.460
Readable.

10:55.940 --> 10:56.940
Th-Thanks.

11:15.739 --> 11:17.180
[Xu Huaisong's place]

11:17.580 --> 11:20.100
[is so cold and lifeless.]

11:20.100 --> 11:21.379
[So bleak.]

11:40.739 --> 11:42.659
Mr. Xu, are you drinking

11:44.940 --> 11:45.859
black coffee?

11:47.139 --> 11:48.659
Taking big gulps of black coffee,

11:48.659 --> 11:49.859
that's a first for me.

12:00.779 --> 12:01.460
Habit.

12:08.979 --> 12:10.580
For the plagiarism checker,

12:10.859 --> 12:11.779
any thoughts?

12:18.659 --> 12:19.979
[Ruan Yu, oh Ruan Yu,]

12:20.300 --> 12:21.379
[what are you doing?]

12:22.420 --> 12:23.700
Mr. Xu, sorry.

12:23.700 --> 12:24.700
I'll go get the documents.

12:41.019 --> 12:41.540
Uh...

12:41.540 --> 12:43.259
Mr. Xu.

12:43.540 --> 12:46.300
I'll go get the documents.

13:10.180 --> 13:10.820
Mr. Xu.

13:14.300 --> 13:16.060
Well, earlier,

13:16.060 --> 13:17.139
a friend in the industry

13:17.139 --> 13:18.460
already helped me with part

13:18.460 --> 13:19.460
of the plagiarism checker.

13:20.100 --> 13:22.979
I picked out a few examples

13:22.979 --> 13:23.739
that I think could serve

13:23.739 --> 13:24.619
as direction for our rebuttal.

13:25.580 --> 13:26.379
Go on.

13:27.139 --> 13:28.899
The first direction is plot-wise.

13:29.420 --> 13:30.180
Like

13:30.700 --> 13:32.379
what I wrote in chapter ten,

13:32.659 --> 13:34.100
the scenes between the male lead

13:34.100 --> 13:34.940
and some side characters.

13:35.979 --> 13:37.499
The fried chicken scene.

13:42.300 --> 13:43.019
I'm in.

13:44.180 --> 13:46.019
Bring a ladder after school

13:46.619 --> 13:47.779
and put it by the back wall.

13:48.019 --> 13:48.700
What ladder?

13:48.700 --> 13:49.460
What for?

13:49.859 --> 13:50.940
You know exactly what for.

13:51.060 --> 13:52.340
To climb over the wall

13:52.340 --> 13:53.300
and buy fried chicken.

13:53.859 --> 13:55.979
[Xu Huaisong—so aloof, elegant,]

13:56.180 --> 13:57.420
[like he doesn't need food or anything,]

13:57.739 --> 13:59.540
[would he really gang up with them to]

13:59.739 --> 14:01.659
[break rules just for fried chicken?]

14:02.100 --> 14:03.300
Did you finish your homework?

14:03.700 --> 14:04.420
I'm not interested.

14:04.420 --> 14:05.139
Come on.

14:05.139 --> 14:06.340
Forget about your homework.

14:06.659 --> 14:07.540
You're not going?

14:07.899 --> 14:08.379
If you don't go,

14:08.379 --> 14:09.739
I'll give your phone to Old Ruan.

14:10.540 --> 14:11.139
[Oh no.]

14:11.379 --> 14:12.859
[With my dad's temper,]

14:13.019 --> 14:14.139
[Xu Huaisong is done for.]

14:14.899 --> 14:16.659
[No, I need to figure something out.]

14:17.060 --> 14:17.820
Are you going or not?

14:19.460 --> 14:20.340
Thank you, Madam.

14:21.019 --> 14:21.580
When I'm done with it,

14:21.580 --> 14:22.779
I'll return it right away.

14:22.779 --> 14:24.060
No rush. Tell Mr. Ruan he's welcome

14:24.060 --> 14:25.019
to keep the ladder as long as he wants.

14:25.019 --> 14:25.499
Just bring it back

14:25.499 --> 14:26.499
- whenever you have time.
- I've got it.

14:27.139 --> 14:27.940
Thank you.

14:42.779 --> 14:43.619
Xu Huaisong.

14:44.619 --> 14:45.259
Now they won't

14:45.259 --> 14:46.420
give you a hard time, right?

14:59.700 --> 15:01.300
Even if it actually happened,

15:01.540 --> 15:02.739
it's been so many years.

15:03.300 --> 15:04.460
He probably doesn't remember it anyway.

15:06.700 --> 15:07.859
What about this scene?

15:10.619 --> 15:11.460
This scene

15:11.460 --> 15:12.700
is also in The Poet's writing.

15:12.820 --> 15:13.899
But if you look closely,

15:13.899 --> 15:14.979
you'll know our intentions in writing it

15:14.979 --> 15:16.100
are completely different.

15:16.420 --> 15:17.820
My version is from

15:17.820 --> 15:19.019
the female lead's perspective,

15:19.019 --> 15:20.259
I wanna reflect her feelings of secret love.

15:20.659 --> 15:21.580
But for The Poet,

15:21.580 --> 15:22.619
it's from the male lead's perspective,

15:22.940 --> 15:23.700
followed by

15:23.700 --> 15:24.820
his internal monologue,

15:25.019 --> 15:26.739
saying he actually loves fried chicken,

15:26.739 --> 15:27.739
but only pretended to be aloof

15:27.739 --> 15:29.019
because the female lead was nearby

15:29.019 --> 15:30.220
and he thought climbing over the wall

15:30.220 --> 15:31.019
was embarrassing.

15:31.019 --> 15:32.220
That's why he acted

15:32.220 --> 15:33.100
like he was above such things.

15:33.420 --> 15:34.139
I think The Poet

15:34.139 --> 15:34.859
included this scene

15:34.859 --> 15:35.499
to highlight

15:35.499 --> 15:36.540
the male lead's duplicity.

15:40.739 --> 15:41.739
Are you okay, Mr. Xu?

16:18.979 --> 16:19.779
So…

16:20.779 --> 16:22.499
Did you return the ladder afterwards?

16:23.379 --> 16:24.300
Did you get punished?

16:27.379 --> 16:28.460
He's asking about me,

16:28.979 --> 16:30.259
not the female lead in the book.

16:31.619 --> 16:32.220
Could he have already

16:32.220 --> 16:33.180
seen my Weibo

16:33.379 --> 16:33.940
and know that this is

16:33.940 --> 16:34.899
my personal experience?

16:41.340 --> 16:42.340
Mr. Xu,

16:42.940 --> 16:44.420
have you seen my Weibo?

16:45.180 --> 16:45.859
No.

16:46.820 --> 16:48.019
Is there something on your Weibo

16:48.019 --> 16:49.460
I should pay special attention to?

16:50.060 --> 16:50.659
If so,

16:50.979 --> 16:52.019
I can take a look now.

16:52.139 --> 16:52.779
No, no.

16:53.180 --> 16:54.499
It's all trivial stuff.

16:54.499 --> 16:55.659
Nothing important.

16:56.619 --> 16:57.259
Let's continue.

16:58.580 --> 16:59.619
Where were we?

17:00.899 --> 17:02.220
When I returned the ladder...

17:06.739 --> 17:07.540
No.

17:07.899 --> 17:09.899
You've totally confused me.

17:11.580 --> 17:12.859
Let me clarify,

17:13.340 --> 17:14.379
what we're talking about now

17:14.580 --> 17:15.619
isn't me,

17:16.540 --> 17:17.500
We're talking about

17:17.820 --> 17:19.219
the protagonist in my novel.

17:19.780 --> 17:21.219
Besides, your question

17:21.580 --> 17:22.219
doesn't really have anything to do

17:22.219 --> 17:23.219
with our case, does it?

17:25.100 --> 17:25.859
Ms. Ruan,

17:26.939 --> 17:28.219
in order to reach a resolution

17:28.219 --> 17:29.820
that satisfies both of us,

17:30.020 --> 17:31.139
as your legal counsel,

17:31.139 --> 17:32.020
I need you to

17:32.020 --> 17:33.379
trust me one hundred percent,

17:33.939 --> 17:34.340
rather than

17:34.340 --> 17:35.619
questioning my professional judgment.

17:42.540 --> 17:43.100
So…

17:43.820 --> 17:45.820
What does whether the female lead

17:46.659 --> 17:47.419
was punished

17:47.419 --> 17:48.740
have to do with our case?

17:51.179 --> 17:52.139
The Poet included

17:52.740 --> 17:53.459
the next day, the male lead saw

17:53.820 --> 17:55.580
the female lead standing in punishment.

17:56.740 --> 17:58.260
If your female lead

17:58.780 --> 17:59.659
was also punished...

18:02.060 --> 18:03.740
Good thing I didn't include that part

18:03.939 --> 18:05.300
'cause I thought she'd suffered enough.

18:06.820 --> 18:08.540
Mr. Xu, you have sharp eyes.

18:09.300 --> 18:10.459
I almost wronged you just now.

18:10.459 --> 18:11.300
Sorry about that.

18:16.980 --> 18:18.260
Let's move on to the second point.

18:19.899 --> 18:21.459
The second direction is character-wise.

18:21.980 --> 18:23.340
Even though these two books

18:23.340 --> 18:24.780
share many similar plot devices,

18:24.899 --> 18:26.260
the male lead's character

18:26.260 --> 18:27.419
is actually very different.

18:27.740 --> 18:29.859
In my novel, the male lead...

18:35.419 --> 18:38.219
In my novel, the male lead

18:40.260 --> 18:41.459
is quiet and elegant,

18:42.139 --> 18:43.219
mature and composed.

18:44.219 --> 18:45.699
Even though he's aloof,

18:46.459 --> 18:48.340
he's gentle at heart,

18:50.020 --> 18:52.859
and a well-rounded top student.

19:12.379 --> 19:12.980
Huaisong.

19:14.500 --> 19:16.139
I reread Senior

19:16.139 --> 19:17.179
Ruan Yu's novel,

19:17.980 --> 19:19.100
and how come in her book,

19:19.419 --> 19:20.419
you've become such a

19:20.419 --> 19:21.379
lofty and unattainable person?

19:26.500 --> 19:27.139
Huaisong.

19:27.699 --> 19:28.780
Were you just putting on an act

19:28.780 --> 19:30.100
in front of her every day back then?

19:32.780 --> 19:33.980
It seems

19:34.179 --> 19:35.780
Ruan Yu likes

19:35.939 --> 19:36.939
that type.

19:37.300 --> 19:38.980
You better watch out,

19:39.139 --> 19:40.340
don't let your persona collapse.

19:41.340 --> 19:42.619
Did your homework not keep you busy enough?

19:54.699 --> 19:57.100
But the male lead

19:58.340 --> 19:59.780
in The Poet's novel...

20:01.540 --> 20:03.980
If my male lead's demeanor

20:04.379 --> 20:05.740
is more like

20:05.939 --> 20:07.459
Hanazawa Rui

20:07.899 --> 20:08.780
from Meteor Garden,

20:09.820 --> 20:11.699
then The Poet's male lead

20:12.659 --> 20:13.939
is more like

20:15.699 --> 20:17.139
Domyoji Tsukasa

20:17.139 --> 20:18.020
from Meteor Garden.

20:31.219 --> 20:31.980
Don't touch it.

20:32.100 --> 20:33.139
This is for Ruan Yu.

20:33.379 --> 20:34.419
Ruan Yu?

20:34.419 --> 20:35.100
Again?

20:35.100 --> 20:36.020
This is for her too?

20:36.459 --> 20:37.619
You're always giving her gifts.

20:38.540 --> 20:39.300
You bet.

20:43.500 --> 20:44.100
Girl.

20:44.740 --> 20:45.740
I saw your favorite grilled corn

20:45.740 --> 20:47.139
at the cafeteria just now.

20:48.219 --> 20:48.859
Here.

20:50.580 --> 20:51.179
No need.

20:51.699 --> 20:52.500
It's you again.

20:52.740 --> 20:54.260
So what if you're "Class 10's Domyoji"?

20:54.540 --> 20:55.100
Who do you think you are,

20:55.100 --> 20:56.340
some kind of domineering CEO?

20:56.740 --> 20:57.698
So childish.

20:57.699 --> 20:59.459
So childish.

20:59.459 --> 21:00.419
What are you guys looking at?

21:01.419 --> 21:01.939
Don't you know Ruan Yu

21:01.939 --> 21:02.939
is the one I've set my sights on?

21:07.939 --> 21:08.540
I'm already being nice

21:08.540 --> 21:09.699
by not telling my dad

21:09.699 --> 21:11.020
about you.

21:11.300 --> 21:13.020
If you keep pestering me

21:13.020 --> 21:14.219
and interrupting my studies,

21:14.219 --> 21:14.659
we'll

21:14.659 --> 21:16.219
take this to the dean's office.

21:17.139 --> 21:17.939
Ruan Yu, Ruan Yu.

21:18.340 --> 21:18.820
Ruan Yu.

21:21.219 --> 21:21.859
And one more thing,

21:22.699 --> 21:23.820
so what if you're Domyoji?

21:24.500 --> 21:26.980
I like Hanazawa Rui.

21:35.820 --> 21:36.580
Sorry,

21:37.020 --> 21:37.939
what did you just say?

21:40.500 --> 21:41.740
I might have made it too complicated.

21:42.139 --> 21:43.619
To sum it up simply,

21:43.939 --> 21:45.340
I think The Poet's male lead

21:45.340 --> 21:46.580
is very playful and childish.

21:47.740 --> 21:49.139
Aren't most boys that age

21:49.699 --> 21:50.699
pretty much the same?

21:52.060 --> 21:52.820
How are they the same?

21:52.820 --> 21:53.980
How can they be the same?

21:54.619 --> 21:55.540
The Poet's male lead

21:55.540 --> 21:57.020
is so different from mine.

21:57.500 --> 21:58.179
Look at him, going to great lengths

21:58.179 --> 21:58.980
for fried chicken and soda

21:58.980 --> 21:59.980
all the time.

22:00.659 --> 22:01.820
Isn't that playful?

22:03.859 --> 22:04.659
And to win the female lead's favor,

22:04.659 --> 22:05.659
he puts on an act

22:05.659 --> 22:06.740
in front of her

22:06.740 --> 22:07.459
every single day.

22:07.540 --> 22:08.540
Isn't that childish?

22:09.020 --> 22:09.820
That's nothing like my male lead,

22:09.820 --> 22:10.780
not at all.

22:11.379 --> 22:11.820
I remember there are

22:11.820 --> 22:13.020
more scenes to prove it.

22:13.139 --> 22:14.379
Wait, let me show you.

22:14.379 --> 22:15.139
No need.

22:16.100 --> 22:17.419
That's it for today's meeting.

22:17.980 --> 22:18.820
We'll continue another day.

22:28.100 --> 22:29.859
He just hung up like that?

22:33.580 --> 22:35.659
Why does he seem kind of upset?

22:38.659 --> 22:40.139
I wasn't talking about him.

22:58.899 --> 23:00.300
[Daydreaming, buddy?]

23:00.659 --> 23:01.699
[Asking a question like that]

23:02.100 --> 23:03.300
[guarantees you'll never]

23:03.300 --> 23:04.659
[be an aloof man in this lifetime.]

23:05.260 --> 23:06.780
[Aloof, elegant,]

23:06.980 --> 23:08.379
[and always confident.]

23:33.899 --> 23:35.020
How to be aloof?

23:47.179 --> 23:47.740
[Something's off.]

23:49.740 --> 23:50.740
[Very off.]

23:58.659 --> 24:00.500
Lawyer Xu, are you asleep?

24:19.300 --> 24:20.219
Nothing urgent.

24:20.780 --> 24:22.020
I just wanted to ask,

24:22.580 --> 24:23.740
during today's meeting,

24:24.060 --> 24:25.459
did I say something wrong?

24:26.340 --> 24:27.260
Why did you suddenly

24:27.859 --> 24:28.699
hang up the video call?

24:43.060 --> 24:43.580
You didn't.

24:44.179 --> 24:45.780
I received an urgent work assignment.

24:48.980 --> 24:50.179
But Ms. Ruan,

24:50.699 --> 24:51.500
you harshly criticized

24:51.500 --> 24:52.740
the other male lead

24:52.899 --> 24:54.300
with strong personal feelings.

24:54.899 --> 24:55.820
You were in a subjective

24:55.820 --> 24:56.939
and irrational state, so we should

24:57.340 --> 24:58.500
postpone discussing the case.

25:00.100 --> 25:01.179
I see.

25:02.740 --> 25:04.020
That's too strict.

25:10.260 --> 25:11.459
Lawyer Xu, you misunderstood me.

25:12.100 --> 25:13.179
I was just

25:13.340 --> 25:14.179
a bit anxious

25:14.179 --> 25:15.419
because you didn't see the difference

25:15.699 --> 25:16.540
between the two male leads.

25:32.139 --> 25:32.699
I do see it.

25:40.699 --> 25:42.500
[She doesn't like me at all.]

25:45.020 --> 25:46.340
[How can I confess my feelings?]

25:55.100 --> 25:56.659
Elite lawyers are different, huh?

25:56.659 --> 25:57.340
Always have to stay

25:57.340 --> 25:58.780
objective and rational.

25:59.459 --> 26:00.379
Did he schedule

26:00.379 --> 26:01.619
the next meeting with you?

26:03.459 --> 26:03.980
No.

26:04.939 --> 26:05.500
Hopefully he's

26:05.500 --> 26:06.859
tied up with some big case

26:07.379 --> 26:08.300
and doesn't have much time

26:08.300 --> 26:09.540
for another video meeting with me.

26:10.020 --> 26:11.100
It feels like

26:11.100 --> 26:12.300
I'm back in school taking an exam.

26:15.699 --> 26:16.699
That's not impossible.

26:16.780 --> 26:18.020
I looked him up.

26:18.379 --> 26:19.300
The SG copyright case

26:19.300 --> 26:20.260
he handled in the US

26:20.260 --> 26:22.699
set foreign media ablaze back then.

26:22.859 --> 26:25.300
They said the young and promising

26:25.300 --> 26:26.580
Lawyer Xu, single-handedly,

26:26.580 --> 26:28.379
brought SG back from the brink.

26:29.419 --> 26:30.060
Word is,

26:30.060 --> 26:31.619
what SG pays him now

26:31.619 --> 26:32.980
as legal counsel

26:32.980 --> 26:34.179
is enough to set him up

26:34.179 --> 26:35.340
for the rest of his life.

26:36.619 --> 26:37.300
That impressive?

26:39.100 --> 26:39.699
Makes my years of

26:39.699 --> 26:40.580
crushing on him worth it.

26:41.500 --> 26:42.100
Proves

26:42.379 --> 26:43.540
I've got pretty good taste.

26:43.939 --> 26:45.780
Good taste alone won't cut it.

26:46.060 --> 26:47.100
He's so sharp,

26:47.740 --> 26:49.219
are you sure you haven't slipped up?

26:52.659 --> 26:53.699
Thanks, miss.

26:53.699 --> 26:54.580
I'll try it on myself.

26:54.859 --> 26:55.340
Okay.

27:00.020 --> 27:00.859
Not yet.

27:02.020 --> 27:02.780
You know what,

27:03.020 --> 27:03.980
to not expose myself,

27:03.980 --> 27:05.100
I have to outwit him every day,

27:05.100 --> 27:05.820
it's exhausting.

27:06.419 --> 27:07.100
One video call

27:07.100 --> 27:08.340
feels like I've run 800 meters.

27:10.100 --> 27:11.340
But after all these years,

27:12.580 --> 27:13.699
he hasn't changed much.

27:15.179 --> 27:16.939
I can hear a hint of

27:16.939 --> 27:18.980
lingering affection.

27:22.580 --> 27:23.500
No way.

27:26.060 --> 27:27.060
How is there not?

27:27.540 --> 27:28.619
Look at you every time

27:28.619 --> 27:30.060
you mention Xu Huaisong,

27:30.060 --> 27:31.300
your emotions fluctuate

27:31.300 --> 27:32.619
just like when you were eighteen.

27:35.580 --> 27:37.300
Who wouldn't get emotional

27:37.300 --> 27:38.619
over something this absurd?

27:39.980 --> 27:40.780
Besides,

27:41.020 --> 27:42.340
love at twenty-eight

27:42.740 --> 27:44.179
can't be like it was at eighteen,

27:44.659 --> 27:46.219
where hormonal urges were enough.

27:47.260 --> 27:48.419
It's not just about charm and

27:48.419 --> 27:49.419
physical attraction,

27:50.100 --> 27:51.580
but also personality in daily interaction,

27:52.219 --> 27:53.740
aligned values mentally,

27:54.020 --> 27:55.139
and a spiritual connection.

27:55.859 --> 27:56.859
These four conditions

27:57.020 --> 27:58.020
are all indispensable.

28:00.020 --> 28:01.540
My little emotional outburst

28:02.379 --> 28:03.899
is far from a rekindled flame.

28:04.780 --> 28:06.060
At most,

28:07.459 --> 28:08.859
it's just nostalgia for youth,

28:10.219 --> 28:11.379
a fond remembrance

28:12.419 --> 28:13.859
of the self I was back then.

28:14.580 --> 28:16.060
No wonder you're a writer.

28:16.859 --> 28:18.419
Four conditions,

28:18.419 --> 28:20.020
and nostalgia and remembrance?

28:20.619 --> 28:21.939
You draw the line so clearly.

28:23.060 --> 28:23.780
But still, he was someone

28:23.780 --> 28:25.300
you had such a huge crush on back then.

28:25.540 --> 28:28.419
You should feel a bit familiar, at least?

28:31.179 --> 28:32.060
Here I am,

28:32.060 --> 28:33.219
holding onto my disguise for dear life.

28:33.219 --> 28:33.859
How could I possibly

28:33.859 --> 28:35.060
feel any closeness to him?

28:36.139 --> 28:36.859
Besides,

28:37.260 --> 28:38.699
it's been ten years.

28:39.300 --> 28:40.540
Now, I only see him as

28:40.859 --> 28:41.419
a responsible,

28:41.419 --> 28:42.939
competent lawyer.

28:43.419 --> 28:44.619
He'd better not be so responsible.

28:44.939 --> 28:45.939
It'd be best if he hands

28:45.939 --> 28:47.020
my case to Lawyer Liu.

28:48.300 --> 28:49.179
What about Lawyer Liu?

28:49.659 --> 28:51.340
You've worked with him for a few days.

28:51.580 --> 28:53.699
Did sparks of love

28:53.699 --> 28:55.500
ignite between you two?

28:57.580 --> 28:58.780
Forget it, with my current situation,

28:58.780 --> 28:59.859
I have no mood for love.

28:59.859 --> 29:01.139
Even if I wanted to fall in love,

29:01.459 --> 29:02.100
Lawyer Liu isn't

29:02.100 --> 29:03.179
my type at all.

29:03.740 --> 29:04.619
How do you know

29:04.619 --> 29:05.939
if you don't try?

29:06.340 --> 29:07.260
Look at me and Zhang Chuan,

29:07.260 --> 29:08.020
when we first got together,

29:08.020 --> 29:08.820
I couldn't stand him.

29:09.020 --> 29:09.939
But look how it turned out.

29:11.659 --> 29:12.459
So good.

29:13.820 --> 29:14.580
It does smell nice.

29:15.500 --> 29:16.100
Hi. Can I get

29:16.379 --> 29:17.500
a bottle of this perfume, please?

29:17.500 --> 29:18.020
Sure.

29:25.419 --> 29:26.100
What's wrong?

29:27.100 --> 29:28.740
I feel like someone's watching us.

29:28.980 --> 29:29.619
It's weird.

29:30.459 --> 29:31.540
It's broad daylight.

29:31.899 --> 29:33.060
Are you switching from romance

29:33.060 --> 29:34.300
to horror?

29:35.260 --> 29:36.060
Just pick your perfume.

29:36.980 --> 29:37.459
Which one?

29:37.459 --> 29:38.740
- This one.
- Senior Ruan.

29:40.020 --> 29:41.060
It's really you.

29:53.580 --> 29:54.580
Excuse me, who are you?

29:55.780 --> 29:57.340
I'm Cen Sisi!

29:57.419 --> 29:58.619
Don't you remember me?

30:09.300 --> 30:10.540
Oh my gosh.

30:10.859 --> 30:12.740
I haven't seen you in ages!

30:13.060 --> 30:13.899
I was just over there

30:13.899 --> 30:14.780
peeking at you for ages. I was afraid

30:14.780 --> 30:16.179
I'd mistaken you for someone else.

30:17.219 --> 30:17.980
Did you end up staying

30:17.980 --> 30:19.219
in Hang City after graduation?

30:21.300 --> 30:22.219
This is our college junior,

30:22.219 --> 30:22.939
Cen Sisi.

30:23.219 --> 30:24.340
She was in the Chinese department too.

30:24.980 --> 30:26.699
This is my best friend, Shen Mingying.

30:26.699 --> 30:27.179
Nice to meet you.

30:27.500 --> 30:28.379
You too.

30:30.100 --> 30:31.139
I remember now.

30:31.540 --> 30:33.179
Back then, you two were

30:33.179 --> 30:34.500
both in the Arts Department with Shican,

30:34.500 --> 30:35.139
right?

30:38.379 --> 30:39.980
Shican and I grew up together.

30:40.100 --> 30:41.340
I saw you so many times

30:41.340 --> 30:42.820
when I went to visit him.

30:43.659 --> 30:44.980
Seeing you three spend all day

30:44.980 --> 30:46.179
in the Arts Department,

30:46.419 --> 30:47.100
those were good times.

30:48.379 --> 30:48.859
Oh, right!

30:49.139 --> 30:50.219
He's got a performance

30:50.219 --> 30:51.139
in Hang City in a few days.

30:51.500 --> 30:52.899
Did you make plans to meet up?

30:54.020 --> 30:55.859
We don't keep in touch much now.

30:56.300 --> 30:57.619
I didn't even know he was coming.

30:59.419 --> 31:00.179
Yeah, that's true.

31:00.179 --> 31:01.980
After he returned to China last year,

31:01.980 --> 31:03.020
he's been really busy.

31:03.340 --> 31:04.060
Even his family

31:04.060 --> 31:05.340
hardly gets to see him.

31:06.020 --> 31:07.260
But no matter how busy he is,

31:07.379 --> 31:08.419
he shouldn't forget his old friends,

31:08.419 --> 31:08.939
right?

31:09.740 --> 31:10.260
How about this.

31:10.899 --> 31:11.980
I'll arrange a time with him

31:11.980 --> 31:13.100
and we can all get together.

31:14.020 --> 31:14.740
That okay?

31:18.459 --> 31:19.300
Senior.

31:19.619 --> 31:21.379
What do you do for a living now?

31:22.260 --> 31:23.500
I'm kind of a freelancer.

31:25.699 --> 31:27.100
Don't tell me you're a writer.

31:29.780 --> 31:30.540
Not really.

31:30.980 --> 31:32.100
Just an average online writer.

31:32.459 --> 31:32.939
And you?

31:33.219 --> 31:34.939
What job did you get after graduation?

31:36.060 --> 31:36.980
Me?

31:37.899 --> 31:38.899
I just work

31:38.899 --> 31:40.619
at my family's company.

31:42.859 --> 31:43.740
But our school

31:43.740 --> 31:45.100
really produces talented people.

31:45.540 --> 31:47.179
Look at Shican, a big star.

31:47.179 --> 31:48.899
And you, a renowned writer.

31:49.419 --> 31:51.219
I do know a few

31:51.219 --> 31:52.260
online writers.

31:52.899 --> 31:54.020
This circle

31:54.020 --> 31:55.020
seems really tough.

31:55.820 --> 31:57.219
They really have it hard.

31:57.899 --> 31:58.699
I'm okay.

31:59.060 --> 31:59.899
I'm pretty laid-back.

32:00.179 --> 32:01.340
I just write for fun.

32:02.580 --> 32:04.619
Yeah, the online environment

32:04.619 --> 32:05.500
isn't great right now.

32:06.100 --> 32:07.899
It's good you can stay positive.

32:17.740 --> 32:18.899
Sorry, I need to take this.

32:19.260 --> 32:20.580
Yeah, go ahead.

32:25.500 --> 32:26.100
Mr. Xu.

32:26.340 --> 32:26.899
Just got

32:26.899 --> 32:27.939
news from the court.

32:28.419 --> 32:29.300
The case has advanced

32:29.300 --> 32:30.659
to the additional defendant phase.

32:31.379 --> 32:32.139
That fast.

32:33.500 --> 32:34.139
Mr. Xu,

32:34.139 --> 32:35.300
it must be very late there.

32:35.500 --> 32:36.260
Still working?

32:37.060 --> 32:38.580
Insomnia. I'm used to it.

32:40.699 --> 32:41.500
I called

32:41.500 --> 32:42.459
just to ask if,

32:42.939 --> 32:44.179
coincidentally or not,

32:44.980 --> 32:46.260
you might know the defendant.

32:47.619 --> 32:48.340
What?

32:50.820 --> 32:52.219
She's an alum from your department.

32:52.659 --> 32:53.500
Two years behind.

32:53.939 --> 32:54.939
From my college?

32:55.980 --> 32:56.580
Yes.

32:57.300 --> 32:58.419
Her name is Cen Sisi.

32:59.060 --> 32:59.899
Does that ring a bell?

33:07.740 --> 33:08.540
I'm with her now,

33:08.540 --> 33:09.340
having dessert.

33:11.939 --> 33:13.820
It seems like the online smearing

33:13.980 --> 33:14.899
and today's encounter

33:15.580 --> 33:16.659
might not be coincidental.

33:35.300 --> 33:36.980
An open secret in the online lit scene.

33:37.219 --> 33:38.379
Steal a rookie's stories

33:38.580 --> 33:39.780
and concepts, then throw some money

33:40.179 --> 33:41.820
at them to shut them up.

33:42.580 --> 33:43.859
This fake statement...

33:44.179 --> 33:45.100
Does Lily Vale really think

33:45.100 --> 33:46.139
netizens are that stupid?

33:47.379 --> 33:48.780
A whole year without writing,

33:48.820 --> 33:50.020
is it her block,

33:50.020 --> 33:51.340
or nothing left to copy?

33:51.859 --> 33:52.980
Did she really write

33:52.980 --> 33:54.500
those past works herself?

33:58.859 --> 34:00.740
Are you okay?

34:01.500 --> 34:02.179
What's wrong?

34:02.500 --> 34:03.540
Are you feeling unwell?

34:03.540 --> 34:05.060
You look off.

34:07.859 --> 34:08.619
Senior.

34:09.379 --> 34:10.219
What's wrong?

34:10.780 --> 34:11.500
Are you okay?

34:14.580 --> 34:15.379
Sisi,

34:16.100 --> 34:17.420
Are you Su Cheng

34:17.420 --> 34:18.699
from Qianhe?

34:23.299 --> 34:23.819
What...

34:24.540 --> 34:26.779
How do you know that? Are you psychic?

34:29.420 --> 34:30.339
I'm not psychic.

34:30.900 --> 34:31.779
I'm Lily Vale.

34:35.020 --> 34:36.299
You're just coming clean this way?

34:36.980 --> 34:38.100
I might as well get a judge in here

34:38.100 --> 34:39.179
to hold a trial for you two.

34:43.299 --> 34:43.940
Senior,

34:44.420 --> 34:46.020
are you joking?

35:03.580 --> 35:05.860
The world is so small.

35:06.580 --> 35:07.060
Then

35:07.339 --> 35:08.219
on Weibo, I...

35:11.779 --> 35:12.500
Oh my god.

35:12.940 --> 35:13.779
Oh my god, oh my god.

35:14.460 --> 35:15.339
Let me calm down.

35:21.580 --> 35:23.179
Senior, this is

35:23.900 --> 35:25.420
a huge misunderstanding!

35:27.100 --> 35:28.739
If I had known Lily Vale was you,

35:28.739 --> 35:29.540
there's no way I would've

35:29.540 --> 35:30.659
posted that Weibo.

35:33.739 --> 35:34.339
Really?

35:35.540 --> 35:36.219
Why is that?

35:36.739 --> 35:37.540
You'd never

35:37.540 --> 35:38.980
do something like plagiarizing.

35:40.900 --> 35:41.580
Senior.

35:42.699 --> 35:44.380
Did you really sue me?

35:48.540 --> 35:51.060
Oh, this is a huge misunderstanding.

35:51.819 --> 35:52.659
If I had known

35:52.659 --> 35:53.739
Su Cheng was you,

35:53.980 --> 35:54.619
I would've...

35:55.460 --> 35:56.779
Sued you sooner.

35:58.819 --> 36:00.299
I was in the wrong anyway.

36:00.299 --> 36:00.900
Senior.

36:03.060 --> 36:04.299
I didn't want this to blow up.

36:05.020 --> 36:05.779
If you really think

36:05.779 --> 36:06.699
this is a misunderstanding,

36:06.980 --> 36:08.060
we could consider settling.

36:08.060 --> 36:09.139
Really?

36:10.139 --> 36:11.100
That would be great.

36:11.619 --> 36:12.580
If my dad finds out

36:12.580 --> 36:13.139
about this,

36:13.139 --> 36:14.219
he'll kill me.

36:15.339 --> 36:17.219
And if Shican finds out too,

36:17.739 --> 36:19.339
he'd be in such a bind.

36:23.819 --> 36:24.500
Senior,

36:24.860 --> 36:26.460
if you're willing to forgive me,

36:26.460 --> 36:28.020
I'll publicly apologize to you,

36:28.020 --> 36:28.900
and try to undo

36:28.900 --> 36:30.139
all the negative impact on you.

36:30.139 --> 36:30.739
I'll never

36:30.739 --> 36:31.699
be that stupid again.

36:31.980 --> 36:32.980
I'll do anything

36:32.980 --> 36:33.779
for you.

36:34.060 --> 36:36.380
So you know you messed up, huh?

36:37.020 --> 36:37.819
It's not a big deal.

36:38.580 --> 36:39.339
But I really don't know

36:39.339 --> 36:41.380
much about the settlement process.

36:47.500 --> 36:48.900
It needs to be discussed with a lawyer.

36:48.900 --> 36:50.100
If we mess it up,

36:50.100 --> 36:51.219
we'll only create

36:51.339 --> 36:52.580
more trouble for ourselves later.

36:52.779 --> 36:55.060
Right. Legal matters

36:55.299 --> 36:56.020
aren't something

36:56.020 --> 36:56.860
we can handle on our own.

36:59.299 --> 37:00.219
Are you free tomorrow?

37:01.860 --> 37:02.460
Tomorrow?

37:04.299 --> 37:04.900
Well...

37:06.100 --> 37:07.179
I have a full day meeting

37:07.179 --> 37:08.500
at the company tomorrow.

37:08.619 --> 37:09.659
I might not be able to make it.

37:10.020 --> 37:11.420
Senior, how about the day after?

37:12.299 --> 37:12.940
That works too.

37:14.219 --> 37:14.699
So,

37:15.299 --> 37:16.259
the court...

37:17.299 --> 37:18.819
I can ask them to pause the proceedings.

37:18.819 --> 37:19.699
Don't worry.

37:21.940 --> 37:22.819
Let's add each other on WeChat.

37:22.819 --> 37:23.819
Stay in touch.

37:23.819 --> 37:24.339
Yeah.

37:38.100 --> 37:39.060
Here's a summary

37:39.060 --> 37:40.299
of my conversation with Su Cheng.

37:40.540 --> 37:41.900
Please take a look.

37:46.259 --> 37:47.420
Judging from the conversation,

37:47.659 --> 37:48.940
Cen Sisi probably really didn't know

37:48.940 --> 37:49.980
you're Lily Vale.

38:11.339 --> 38:12.020
I don't think so.

38:14.179 --> 38:15.259
This is complicated.

38:15.819 --> 38:16.900
Let's talk about it face to face tomorrow.

38:17.299 --> 38:18.420
What time works for you both?

38:25.100 --> 38:26.299
Is 1 p.m. tomorrow okay?

38:27.940 --> 38:29.100
Fine by me.

38:29.460 --> 38:30.380
Lawyer Xu?

38:38.339 --> 38:39.580
Push it back four hours.

38:42.060 --> 38:43.460
It's midnight for you.

38:45.900 --> 38:47.179
My schedule is flexible.

38:47.460 --> 38:48.739
We'll go with your time, Lawyer Xu.

38:51.299 --> 38:52.339
Alright, Ruan Yu.

38:52.739 --> 38:53.420
So tomorrow,

38:53.420 --> 38:54.659
let's meet at the office at 5 p.m.

39:02.139 --> 39:02.619
Thanks.

39:03.500 --> 39:04.659
Thank you. Thank you.

39:04.659 --> 39:05.699
Okay, this way.

39:11.299 --> 39:11.940
Mr. Xu,

39:13.860 --> 39:14.980
we can't thank you enough.

39:15.060 --> 39:15.779
Without your help,

39:16.500 --> 39:17.380
we foreigners stuck here

39:17.380 --> 39:18.179
would have been

39:18.819 --> 39:19.179
taken advantage of

39:19.179 --> 39:20.139
so badly.

39:21.339 --> 39:22.219
The purpose of law

39:22.779 --> 39:24.299
is to fairly protect

39:24.299 --> 39:25.420
and provide relief to the innocent.

39:26.699 --> 39:27.460
That's what we lawyers

39:27.460 --> 39:28.100
should do.

39:29.779 --> 39:30.819
That's the theory.

39:31.940 --> 39:32.699
But we're just poor

39:32.699 --> 39:33.500
wage earners.

39:33.739 --> 39:34.339
It's only you who's willing

39:34.339 --> 39:35.380
to take our case pro bono,

39:36.460 --> 39:36.980
and you've done so much

39:36.980 --> 39:38.100
for us all along the way.

39:38.739 --> 39:40.500
Anyway, thank you.

39:40.940 --> 39:41.659
Thank you.

39:42.699 --> 39:43.580
When you're away from home,

39:43.940 --> 39:45.219
you have to rely on your own people.

39:45.980 --> 39:46.500
Alright.

39:47.060 --> 39:48.139
I won't take up your work time.

39:48.460 --> 39:49.060
I'll be leaving now.

40:03.980 --> 40:04.460
Hello.

40:04.699 --> 40:05.659
Song.

40:06.100 --> 40:07.339
I'm so mad!

40:07.540 --> 40:09.299
That Su Cheng actually urged me

40:09.299 --> 40:10.699
to sue Senior Ruan Yu.

40:12.460 --> 40:13.219
I'll send you the screenshot.

40:17.100 --> 40:18.139
After thinking it over,

40:18.179 --> 40:19.659
I still suggest you sue Lily Vale.

40:19.900 --> 40:20.860
After all, she infringed

40:20.860 --> 40:21.779
on your copyright.

40:22.420 --> 40:22.980
Huaishi, you're new

40:23.219 --> 40:24.619
to the online literature market.

40:24.819 --> 40:26.619
You don't know how much damage

40:26.739 --> 40:27.460
her plagiarism

40:27.460 --> 40:28.779
will cause you down the line.

40:30.020 --> 40:30.779
See?

40:32.540 --> 40:33.580
What do I do then?

40:34.460 --> 40:35.580
Make her prove

40:36.179 --> 40:37.380
that she's actually Su Cheng.

40:55.179 --> 40:56.699
Lawyer Xu is probably asleep by now.

40:57.060 --> 40:58.219
It's midnight for him.

41:00.020 --> 41:00.699
Right.

41:00.860 --> 41:01.739
Then let's not wait for him.

41:02.259 --> 41:03.900
Don't worry. Even without Lawyer Xu,

41:03.900 --> 41:05.219
you still have Lawyer Liu here.

41:05.460 --> 41:05.980
Let's continue

41:06.900 --> 41:08.420
from where we left off yesterday.

41:09.060 --> 41:09.580
Okay.

41:11.739 --> 41:12.980
Cen Sisi gave me the impression

41:12.980 --> 41:14.219
that she was overacting.

41:14.739 --> 41:15.420
After I told her

41:15.420 --> 41:16.380
I was Lily Vale,

41:16.699 --> 41:17.619
she suddenly jerked her chin

41:17.619 --> 41:18.500
down onto the glass.

41:18.980 --> 41:19.699
Her eyes even

41:19.699 --> 41:20.699
started to water from the pain.

41:21.179 --> 41:22.739
She rubbed it for a while before saying,

41:23.259 --> 41:24.739
"Are you joking?"—that kind of thing.

41:25.100 --> 41:26.940
Also, after being exposed,

41:26.940 --> 41:27.900
her face turned bright red,

41:27.900 --> 41:29.100
and she kept fanning herself.

41:29.659 --> 41:31.420
At the time, these gestures

41:31.739 --> 41:33.100
just made her seem shocked,

41:33.739 --> 41:35.339
but the more I thought about it,

41:35.339 --> 41:36.380
the more off it felt.

41:37.219 --> 41:38.940
You mean she was faking it all?

41:40.619 --> 41:41.900
She probably didn't expect

41:42.139 --> 41:43.420
me to be so direct.

41:44.219 --> 41:45.819
So I think her exaggerated actions

41:46.940 --> 41:47.659
were meant

41:47.659 --> 41:49.100
to distract me

41:49.339 --> 41:50.380
and buy herself time

41:50.380 --> 41:51.500
to craft her response.

41:55.060 --> 41:55.819
So, I think

41:57.100 --> 41:58.580
she has another trick up her sleeve.

42:00.219 --> 42:00.980
Another trick?

42:02.819 --> 42:03.699
No way.

42:04.259 --> 42:05.580
She can't have that many tricks.

42:05.619 --> 42:06.940
You writers

42:06.940 --> 42:08.179
must have too vivid imaginations.

42:10.500 --> 42:11.940
But her actions

42:12.060 --> 42:12.860
really...

42:17.900 --> 42:18.380
Xu...

42:19.139 --> 42:20.179
Mr. Xu?

42:23.699 --> 42:24.699
Why are you back in the country?

42:25.659 --> 42:26.860
I thought you said at the office?

42:32.659 --> 42:33.299
What's this?

42:35.420 --> 42:36.980
Cen Sisi's next move.

43:03.020 --> 43:04.020
Let's get some fried chicken

43:04.020 --> 43:05.139
this afternoon.

43:05.139 --> 43:06.060
Sounds good.

43:06.339 --> 43:07.540
Fried chicken? Huaisong.

43:07.699 --> 43:08.060
You, as a

43:08.060 --> 43:09.299
smart and sensible student,

43:09.299 --> 43:10.540
always dragging us to do these things,

43:10.540 --> 43:11.380
is that appropriate?

43:11.819 --> 43:12.900
Do you want it or not?

43:13.139 --> 43:14.020
Yeah, I'm in.

43:15.299 --> 43:16.860
Bring a ladder after school

43:17.420 --> 43:18.339
and put it

43:18.420 --> 43:19.219
by the back wall.

43:20.580 --> 43:22.060
What ladder?

43:22.500 --> 43:23.580
Find a ladder

43:23.900 --> 43:25.100
and put it by the back wall.

43:26.179 --> 43:26.860
What are you talking about?

43:27.420 --> 43:28.460
You know exactly what for.

43:28.460 --> 43:29.699
To climb over the wall

43:29.699 --> 43:30.819
and buy fried chicken.

43:30.819 --> 43:32.060
Did you finish your homework?

43:32.380 --> 43:32.779
I'm not interested.

43:32.779 --> 43:34.100
What? Come on.

43:34.100 --> 43:35.060
Forget about your homework.

43:35.060 --> 43:36.179
Let's go get some fried chicken!

43:37.619 --> 43:39.819
Come on, are we doing this or not?

43:39.819 --> 43:41.259
Hurry up, they'll close soon.

43:41.540 --> 43:42.619
You get the ladder.

43:42.900 --> 43:43.900
What's wrong with you?

43:45.699 --> 43:46.460
Deal.

43:46.819 --> 43:47.940
keep your voices down.

43:49.020 --> 43:50.060
No one's going to mistake you

43:50.060 --> 43:51.420
for mute if you keep quiet.

43:51.420 --> 43:52.380
What? We've always

43:52.380 --> 43:53.179
talked like this!

43:53.179 --> 43:54.659
We're just loud!

43:55.299 --> 43:56.500
You never complained before.

43:56.900 --> 43:57.380
Don't you talk like this too?

43:57.380 --> 43:58.219
So are we

43:58.219 --> 43:59.580
eating fried chicken or not?

44:00.540 --> 44:01.980
Yeah, yeah.

44:02.060 --> 44:03.339
Let's go! Fried chicken!
